properties.areaDesc: Admiralty Inlet Area; Eastern Strait of Juan de Fuca
properties.headline: Winter Storm Warning issued January 12 at 2:01PM PST until January 13 at 6:00AM PST by NWS Seattle WA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Heavy snow expected. Total snow accumulations of up to
4 inches.

* WHERE...Admiralty Inlet Area, including Port Townsend, Whidbey
Island, and Camano Island and Eastern Strait of Juan de Fuca
lowlands, including Port Angeles, Sequim, and Blyn.

* WHEN...Until 6 AM PST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Travel could be very difficult.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...
properties.instruction:
If you must travel, keep an extra flashlight, food, and water in
your vehicle in case of an emergency.

For the latest road conditions in Washington state, call 5 1 1.

NWSheadline: WINTER STORM WARNING IN EFFECT UNTIL 6 AM PST MONDAY
